platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Friendly competition with a like-minded sporting community is a big part of Strava’s appeal. More than just a GPS, Strava shares your rides and runs automatically, so it’s low maintenance. See your rank on your favorite segment, join distance challenges, and follow your friends, pros, and even foes. As they say, “If it’s not on Strava, it didn’t happen.”
這款 App 不只是作為 GPS 使用，更能自動分享你的騎乘和跑步路線，而無需親手操作，你還能查看在喜愛路段上的排名、加入距離挑戰，並追蹤你的朋友、專業人士，甚至競爭對手的動態！

Friendly competition with a like-minded sporting community is a big part of Strava's appeal. More than just a GPS, Strava shares your rides and runs automatically, so it's really low maintenance. See your rank on your favourite segment, join distance challenges, and follow your friends, pros and even foes. As they say, "If it’s not on Strava, it didn’t happen".
ただのGPSにとどまらず、サイクリングやランニングの記録を自動で共有する機能を備えた便利なアプリです。お気に入りの区間での自分のランキングをチェックし、距離チャレンジに参加し、友だちやプロ選手、そしてライバルをフォローしましょう。

More than just a GPS, this app shares your rides and runs automatically, so it’s low maintenance. See your rank on your favourite segment, join distance challenges and follow your friends, pros – even foes!

More than just a GPS, this app shares your rides and runs automatically, so it’s low maintenance. See your rank on your favourite segment, join distance challenges, and follow your friends, pros–even foes!
這款 App 不僅僅是 GPS，還能自動分享你的跑步或騎行數據，為你省下手動操作的心力。此外，你也能在 App 查看排名、參加挑戰，與好友或專業運動員互動。

Plus qu’un simple GPS, cette app partage automatiquement vos parcours et courses sans effort de votre part. Consultez votre classement sur votre segment préféré, participez à des défis à distance et suivez vos amis et amies, des pros et même vos adversaires !
